00:29:26.560 --> 00:29:28.640
¿Admites la culpa?

00:29:31.640 --> 00:29:32.959
¿Cuánto quieres?

00:29:32.959 --> 00:29:34.119
Yo, hijo del magistrado de distrito,

00:29:35.359 --> 00:29:36.520
Te lo devolveré.

00:29:37.119 --> 00:29:37.800
Asistentes!

00:29:39.359 --> 00:29:41.719
Llévate este rico Dacong

00:29:41.719 --> 00:29:43.760
y remarle 15 golpes.

00:29:43.760 --> 00:29:47.920
Celebrar juicio en la corte.

00:29:47.920 --> 00:29:48.560
Tu honor,

00:29:49.239 --> 00:29:50.239
yo soy

00:29:51.079 --> 00:29:54.640
El hijo del magistrado de distrito.

00:29:54.640 --> 00:29:56.719
¿Te atreves a vencerme?

00:29:56.719 --> 00:29:58.520
