00:37:29.199 --> 00:37:30.719
Ruyi y yo ...

00:37:30.719 --> 00:37:31.479
Ruyi?

00:37:32.199 --> 00:37:33.360
Ella es mi hermana menor.

00:37:34.360 --> 00:37:35.199
