00:38:08.280 --> 00:38:09.840
¿Ahora que?

00:38:16.520 --> 00:38:17.199
Prima.

00:38:17.959 --> 00:38:20.840
Seré tu primo pronto.

00:38:23.399 --> 00:38:25.520
Oficial Zheng, deténgalo.

00:38:27.919 --> 00:38:30.040
