00:39:09.159 --> 00:39:12.520
Baba, es tu turno.

00:39:12.520 --> 00:39:12.959
Vamos.

00:39:15.040 --> 00:39:15.479
Vamos.

00:39:16.280 --> 00:39:16.719
Déjame solo.

00:39:16.719 --> 00:39:17.399
